  <data name="WelcomeOOBEDialog.Content" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Welcome to Server App Desktop!
This app helps you manage your Minecraft server clearly and easily, whether it is Bedrock or Java. Here you can set up the interface appearance, server folder and executable, connection port, and description.
Everything is organized in simple steps so you can move forward without complications.
You also have features like auto start and customization for a better experience. When you finish this initial setup, your environment will be ready for you and your community.
This is the beginning of your journey: each setting becomes part of your digital space. Explore, enjoy, and get ready to run your server with confidence.</value>
